		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Hellfire Strikes",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The Hellfire Myrmidon attempts Three Strikes against a single Creature with a -2 circumstance malus to its attack roll, combining the damage of all Strikes and applies resistance and weaknesses only once. If a creature is slain by this Strike, theiy'll resurrect as a shade after [[/gmr 1d4 #Duration]]{1d4 hour}. This counts as three attacks for the mulitple attack penalty but the penalty doesn't applies until the hellfire myrmidon has made all Strikes. The Hellfire Myrmidon can't use Hellfire Strikes again for [[/gmr 1d6 #Duration]]{1d6 rounds}.</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
